WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Hello, today I will show you, how to broadcast Wi-Fi from your computer, without any program.

00:00:59.440 --> 00:01:01.440
First step: run the "Commander"- as administrator

00:01:01.440 --> 00:02:00.000
In the commander write this: "netsh wlan set hostednetwork mode =allow ssid="network name" key="password""and press ENTER

00:02:41.800 --> 00:02:52.800
Open: Control panel -&gt; Network and Internet -&gt; Center of network and sharing-&gt; Click on the connection which you exactly connected.

00:03:00.800 --> 00:03:36.853
Click on the "properties"-&gt; sharing -&gt;mark "Enable sharing this internet connection to all users-&gt;settings-&gt; and mark all check boxes and press OK

00:03:36.853 --> 00:03:57.600
Go back to commander and write:"netsh wlan start hostednetwork" and now it broadcast your network, you can check it for example on mobile phone or other  device with Wi-Fi.

00:03:58.100 --> 00:05:31.300
And when you want turn off it, write in commander:"netsh wlan stop hostednetwork".

00:05:31.300 --> 00:05:50.300
THANKS FOR WATCHING AND ENJOY YOUR INTERNET CONNECTION

